-- Globe Telecom Rises in Manila on Higher Sales, Mobile Phone Subscribers
-- B y   I a n   S a y s o n
-- 2011-02-09T02:25:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-09/globe-telecom-rises-in-manila-on-higher-sales-mobile-phone-subscribers.html
  Globe Telecom Inc . climbed the most
among stocks in the benchmark Philippine equities index after
the mobile phone service provider said fourth quarter sales rose
to near a record with the addition of more cellular phone
customers.  Globe advanced 2.7 percent to 800 pesos as of 10:21 a.m. in  Manila , the biggest percentage gain in the Philippine Stock
Exchange Index. The measure fell 0.1 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Sayson in Manila at 
